  Location:
    Page: 336
  Source:
    Title: The Book of Hours
    Location: I 13
By: Rainer Maria Rilke
Title: In Your Sight
Description: December 2
Format: Verse
---
I want to unfold.
Let no place in me hold itself closed,
for where I am closed, I am false.
I want to stay clear in your sight.
